        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_6",
          "href": null,
          "name": "98fa",
          "text": "Healing the soils",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "H4"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_7",
          "href": null,
          "name": "29b3",
          "text": "Tom is the co-editor of a book entitled ‘Geotherapy: Innovative Methods of Soil Fertility Restoration, Carbon Sequestration and Reversing CO2 Increase’. It is an authoritative guide to some of the most cutting edge methods for soil focussed geotherapy.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 150,
              "href": "https://books.google.es/books/about/Geotherapy.html?id=eprNBQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&source=kp_read_button&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 41,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_8",
          "href": null,
          "name": "59c0",
          "text": "",
          "metadata": {
            "id": "1*Xpdpc9m9fGuz5yVuJc6F_w.jpeg",
            "alt": null
          },
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": "OUTSET_LEFT",
          "markups": [],
          "type": "IMG"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_9",
          "href": null,
          "name": "7fce",
          "text": "The book “presents innovative new technologies for restoring the most productive ecosystems on land while maintaining high biodiversity. It addresses processes and techniques of soil carbon restoration through biogeochemical cycling, biochar, slow-release fertilizers, weathering of minerals (olivine) and rock (basalt) powders, amendments and bio-fertilizers, and the establishment of vetiver and other perennials” (more on Tom’s work focused on increasing soil carbon).",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 469,
              "href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sFZPrVSuG84",
              "rel": "noopener",
              "start": 417,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_10",
          "href": null,
          "name": "0dc4",
          "text": "Since 2016 I have met Tom a number of times at the meetings at the Commonwealth Secretariat that I helped to curate through initially the Cloudburst Foundation and now through Common Earth. The initiative was initially called ‘Regenerative Development to Reverse Climate Change’ and has since evolved into ‘Common Earth’.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 91,
              "href": "https://medium.com/activate-the-future/regenerating-the-wealth-of-the-earths-commons-8e30f6c339ac",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 51,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 159,
              "href": "https://www.cloudburstfoundation.org",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 138,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 277,
              "href": "https://thecommonwealth.org/sites/default/files/inline/WorkshopRegenerativeDevelopmentReverseClimateChange.pdf",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 227,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 319,
              "href": "https://common.earth/about",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 307,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_11",
          "href": null,
          "name": "b7cd",
          "text": "“Common Earth catalyses regeneration by working with the Commonwealth to educate around and deliver regenerative pilot projects across the 53 member states. The organization convenes key stakeholders at the Commonwealth Secretariat to learn about cutting-edge regenerative work and to mobilize multilateral support for it. Critically, Common Earth makes regenerative projects accessible in new ways through multimedia storytelling, art exhibitions, and public educational programs.”",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
