          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_24",
          "href": null,
          "name": "b899",
          "text": "Many of his experiments around the world using micro-currents and steel mesh frames to grow marine organisms at increased rate (corals, mussels, oysters, etc)",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_25",
          "href": null,
          "name": "4eae",
          "text": "Application of this method to salt marsh and sea grass regeneration which have a high potential for marine carbon sequestration through building up marine ‘soils’ through burying the roots",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_26",
          "href": null,
          "name": "c776",
          "text": "Applications of such artifical reefs to protect beaches from erosion and even to re-establish beaches",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_27",
          "href": null,
          "name": "db47",
          "text": "Experiments in Italy where his team demonstrated that his technique could regrow seagrasses on bare rock where they normally do not root",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_28",
          "href": null,
          "name": "398f",
          "text": "His work in superfund sites in the US on salt marsh regeneration",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "7899ec8a8698_29",
          "href": null,
          "name": "fb47",
          "text": "The problem of seawalls made from concrete in general and how permeable artificial reefs are much more effective as costal protection",
